code: protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     KubernetesConfiguration config = new KubernetesConfiguration().     setProperties(config, parameters).     config.setMasterUrl(remaining).     if (ObjectHelper.isEmpty(config.getMasterUrl())) {         throw new IllegalArgumentException("Master URL must be specified").     }     return doCreateEndpoint(uri, remaining, config). }
protected abstract AbstractKubernetesEndpoint doCreateEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, KubernetesConfiguration config) throws Exception.
